{{vgname|Among Us|aka=我們之中、在我們之中、我們之間、在我們之間、內鬼殺、太空狼人殺}}，是一款[[多人电子游戏|多人电子游戏]]，可以邀請朋友一同游玩，由[[美国|美国]]<ref name="innersloth">{{Cite web|title=About|url=http://www.innersloth.com/About.php|accessdate=2020-09-09|work=InnerSloth|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123217/http://www.innersloth.com/About.php|archivedate=2020-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>Innersloth工作室开发并于2018年6月15日发布。[[游戏|游戏]]背景设置于[[太空|太空]]或天空，[[玩家|玩家]]将扮演[[船員|船員]]（{{Lang-en|Crewmate}}）或内鬼（{{Lang-en|Impostor}}）之一。船員的目标是找出内鬼并完成任务，而内鬼的目标是杀死或让所有船員被投出局而不被識穿身分。虽然游戏于2018年发布，但鲜有问津，直到2020年因为众多[[Twitch|Twitch]]實況主和[[YouTuber|YouTuber]]游玩才開始流行起来，<ref name=":10">{{Cite web|title=Among Us' Improbable Rise To The Top Of Twitch|url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/09/among-us-improbable-rise-to-the-top-of-twitch/|accessdate=2020-09-30|author=|date=2020-09-08|last=Says|first=Cannon|format=|work=Kotaku Australia|publisher=|language=en-AU|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909025025/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/09/among-us-improbable-rise-to-the-top-of-twitch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但在2022年玩家人數減少了，從2020年9月的6000萬位活躍玩家減至2022年5月的995000至1.1百萬位活躍玩家。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Is Among Us dead in 2022? [latest Among Us player count] |url=https://techacake.com/is-among-us-dead/ |website=techacake.com |language=en |access-date=2022-06-23}}</ref>为回应游戏的热度，游戏开发者于2020年8月宣布将[[开发|开发]]续作《Among Us 2》，但是一个月后（9月）宣布取消续作的开发，将重点转移到改进原版游戏上<ref name=":15">{{Cite web|title=Among Us 2 cancelled as devs focus on original title|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-09-24-among-us-2-cancelled-as-devs-focus-on-original-title|accessdate=2020-09-24|author=Kent|date=2020-09-24|first=Emma|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925235536/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-09-24-among-us-2-cancelled-as-devs-focus-on-original-title|archivedate=2020-09-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":12">{{Cite web|title=The Future of Among Us|url=https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us/devlog/181107/the-future-of-among-us|accessdate=2020-09-23|author=|date=2020-09-23|first=|work=[[Itch.io|Itch.io]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924084429/https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us/devlog/181107/the-future-of-among-us|archivedate=2020-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 遊戲玩法 ==
《Among Us》是一款[[多人遊戲|多人遊戲]]，支援4-15名玩家。其中遊戲將隨機選擇1-3名玩家扮演伪装者，其餘玩家則是扮演船員。

遊戲共有四張[[地圖|地圖]]：

# 太空飛船（{{Lang-en|The Skeld}}）
# 摩天大樓（{{Lang-en|MIRA HQ}}）
# 極地（{{Lang-en|Polus}}）
# 飛艇（{{Lang-en|The Airship}}） (此地圖為 作者的另一個遊戲 [[亨利火柴人|亨利火柴人]] 的部分地圖<ref>{{Cite web|title=《Among Us》PC版 : 新地圖“飛艇”降臨 {{!}} BlueStacks|url=https://www.bluestacks.com/tw/blog/news/among-us-the-airship-map-tw.html|access-date=2022-05-09|date=2020-12-14|work=Bluestacks - The Best Android Emulator on PC as Rated by You|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417104830/https://www.bluestacks.com/tw/blog/news/among-us-the-airship-map-tw.html}}</ref>) 

船員（{{Lang-en|Crewmate}}）要以小遊戲的形式在地圖上完成任務，其中包括對重要系統的維護工作，例如重新佈線或給發動機加油。伪装者（{{Lang-en|Impostor}}）會得到虛假的任務清單以便混在船員之中，伪装者可以識別其他內鬼的身份並有能力破壞地圖系統，穿越通風口和殺死船員。如果玩家被內鬼殺死，他們將變成[[幽靈|幽靈]]。幽靈具有穿過牆壁的能力，但只能以有限的方式繼續在地圖上互動，除了變成幽靈的死亡玩家，其他玩家都無法看見幽靈。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Pearson|first=Craig|date=2020-08-27|title=Among Us has made a lying murderer out of me|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2020/08/27/among-us-has-made-lying-murderer-out-of-me/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909025037/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2020/08/27/among-us-has-made-lying-murderer-out-of-me/|archive-date=2020-09-09|access-date=2020-09-08|website=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|last=Lau|first=Evelyn|date=2020-09-08|title='Among Us': what to know about the online survival game that's all about deceit|url=https://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/among-us-what-to-know-about-the-online-survival-game-that-s-all-about-deceit-1.1074482|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909024952/https://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/among-us-what-to-know-about-the-online-survival-game-that-s-all-about-deceit-1.1074482|archive-date=2020-09-09|access-date=2020-09-08|website=[[The_National_(Abu_Dhabi)|The National]]|language=en}}</ref>。除了幽靈以外<ref>{{Cite web|last=Paez|first=Danny|title=3 'Among Us' ghost tips to help your team win from beyond the grave|url=https://www.inverse.com/gaming/among-us-ghost-tips-how-to-win-crewmate-imposter-ejection|access-date=2020-09-16|website=Inverse|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-21|date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123215/https://www.inverse.com/gaming/among-us-ghost-tips-how-to-win-crewmate-imposter-ejection|dead-url=no}}</ref>，所有玩家都只能看到有限的距離<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|last=Penney|first=Andrew|date=2020-09-16|title=Among Us Review: A Perfect Way To Ruin Your Friendships|url=https://www.thegamer.com/among-us-review/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123255/https://www.thegamer.com/among-us-review/|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-16|website=TheGamer|language=en-US}}</ref>。

船員需要完成所有任務或找到並投票驅逐所有內鬼獲勝，而內鬼則需要殺死一定數量的船員，使剩餘的人數等同內鬼的人數或破壞倒計時結束後獲勝。（但是很多時候玩家會因個人或網路原因掉線，所以伪装者有时只要殺死很少船員就可勝利）幽靈則是通過協助身為船員或伪装者的隊友完成任務或進行破壞。當內鬼進行破壞活動時，要麼立即產生效果（例如關閉所有燈光），要麼被破壞設施將開始倒數計時（例如破壞核反應堆），如果船員沒有在倒計時結束之前完成修理設施，所有船員將死亡並且遊戲結束<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":6" />。

如果某位玩家發現了[[屍體|屍體]]，可以立即通報並強制所有玩家參加小組[[會議|會議]]，[[投票|投票]]選出疑似內鬼的玩家，投票採用[[相對多數制|相對多數制]]，獲得票數最高的玩家將會立即死亡變成幽靈<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" />。如最高票者有多於一個，即平票，或投棄權者超過最高得票者，則無人死亡。幽靈沒有投票權，因為他們知道誰是伪装者，即殺死他們的人。玩家還可以隨時按下地圖上的“緊急會議（{{Lang-en|Emergency meeting}}）”[[按鈕|按鈕]]來召開會議（無論是伪装者還是船員但幽靈不能），不過所有玩家按按鈕的次數有限制，所以不可連續按多次按鈕，以把機會讓給別人，同時防止被濫用以及騷擾。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Marshall|first=Cass|date=2020-09-11|title=Why Among Us’ Emergency Meeting is the big social media mood|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/11/21432684/among-us-emergency-meeting-meme-explained|access-date=2020-09-13|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123243/https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/11/21432684/among-us-emergency-meeting-meme-explained|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Marshall|first=Cass|date=2020-09-18|title=New Among Us players keep accidentally outing themselves as aliens|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/18/21445675/among-us-community-memes-new-players-accidental-guilt|access-date=2020-09-19|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123249/https://www.polygon.com/2020/9/18/21445675/among-us-community-memes-new-players-accidental-guilt|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2" />。遊戲通過文字進行聊天<ref name=":1" />，或者使用“Quick chat”功能进行快捷输入（在新版本中低于13岁的玩家只可以使用“Quick chat”进行聊天）。只有活著的玩家才能在會議期間進行[[交流|交流]]，而幽靈只能在幽靈之間交流<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":5" /><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|last=Matthews|first=Emma|date=2020-09-15|title=Deceive your friends with these sneaky Among Us tips|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/among-us-imposter-crewmate-tips-guide-emergency-meeting/|access-date=2020-09-16|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123245/https://www.pcgamer.com/among-us-imposter-crewmate-tips-guide-emergency-meeting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管遊戲沒有內置的語音聊天系統，但玩家通常會在玩遊戲的同時使用類似[[Discord|Discord]]的第三方聊天工具交流<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|last=Winslow|first=Jeremy|date=2020-09-18|title=Among Us PS4, Xbox One Port More Complicated Than You Think|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/among-us-ps4-xbox-one-port-more-complicated-than-you-think/1100-6482373/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123303/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/among-us-ps4-xbox-one-port-more-complicated-than-you-think/1100-6482373/|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-19|website=GameSpot|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":9">{{Cite web|last=Paez|first=Danny|date=2020-09-17|title=‘Among Us’ dev offers disappointing update on progress for Xbox, PS4 ports|url=https://www.inverse.com/gaming/among-us-xbox-ps4-release-date-update|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123252/https://www.inverse.com/gaming/among-us-xbox-ps4-release-date-update|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-19|website=Inverse|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":10" />。遊戲提供各種自定義選項，例如視野範圍和緊急會議按鈕<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />。遊戲中還有很多物品可以選擇，例如[[航天服|太空服]]顏色、[[皮膚|皮膚]]、[[帽子|帽子]]和[[寵物|寵物]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=Hou|first=Philip|date=2020-09-02|title=Among Us: There’s More to Cosmetics Than You Think|url=https://www.cbr.com/among-us-more-to-cosmetics/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924152952/https://www.cbr.com/among-us-more-to-cosmetics/|archive-date=2020-09-24|access-date=2020-09-22|website=CBR|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Çakır|first=Gökhan|date=2020-09-20|title=Fan makes adorable concept for League x Among Us crossover|url=https://dotesports.com/news/fan-makes-adorable-concept-for-league-x-among-us-crossover|access-date=2020-09-22|website=Dot Esports|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921161145/https://dotesports.com/news/fan-makes-adorable-concept-for-league-x-among-us-crossover|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有其中一部分需要付費<ref name=":5" /><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|last=Carless|first=Simon|date=2020-09-10|title=Behind the dizzying ride to the top for Among Us|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/SimonCarless/20200910/369968/Behind_the_dizzying_ride_to_the_top_for_Among_Us.php|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123258/https://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/SimonCarless/20200910/369968/Behind_the_dizzying_ride_to_the_top_for_Among_Us.php|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-16|website=Gamasutra|language=en}}</ref><ref name="gamerantsequel">{{Cite web|last=Brian|first=Renadette|date=2020-08-19|title=Among Us 2 Announced Following First Game's Huge Surge In Popularity|url=https://gamerant.com/among-us-2-trailer/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909025037/https://gamerant.com/among-us-2-trailer/|archive-date=2020-09-09|access-date=2020-09-08|website=Game Rant|language=en-US}}</ref>{{Efn|“Among Us”的[[手機|手機]]版和[[个人电脑|PC]]版本均有付費[[DLC|DLC]]，其中某些手機版本中的DLC包含在PC標準版內。<ref name=":7" />|name=|group=}}。

船员分为以下角色：

# 普通船员，即完成自己任務，修理破壞，找出內鬼，同時防禦自己
# 工程师，可以與內鬼一起跳管道，但每跳一次后就需要冷却30秒，且只能在管道中停留有限时间。一般遊戲只有一名工程師，所以當發現非工程師跳管道則意味著是偽裝者。
# 守护天使，可以給別人免疫一次死亡的機會
# 科学家，在普通船員的基礎上可以查看玩家的心電圖，可以知道玩家是否還存活，但作用有限，而且心电图在使用3-4秒后就会因电量耗尽锁死。完成任务可以为心电图充电。

偽裝者则分为这些角色：

# 普通伪装者，可以破壞且擊殺船員。
# 變形者，在普通偽裝者的基礎上可以偽裝身分成其他玩家，可以栽贓且防止被發現。<ref name="innersloth" />

== 发展历史 ==
=== 早期開發 ===
《Among Us》受到[[桌上遊戲|桌上遊戲]]《[[杀手_(1986年游戏)|杀手]]》的启发<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":16">{{Cite web|last=Fenlon|first=Wes|date=2020-09-24|title=How Among Us became so wildly popular|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/how-among-us-became-so-popular/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925235535/https://www.pcgamer.com/how-among-us-became-so-popular/|archive-date=2020-09-25|access-date=2020-09-25|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|language=en-US}}</ref>，最初是仅在移动设备发布的一款单一地图的本地多人游戏。<ref name=":7" />

2018年6月，这款游戏发布在[[Android|Android]]和[[iOS|iOS]]上，AppID为“spacemafia”<ref name=":7" /><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Among Us - Apps on Google Play|url=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.innersloth.spacemafia&hl=en_US|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123231/https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.innersloth.spacemafia&hl=en_US|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-13|website=Google Play|language=en}}</ref>。发布后不久，《Among Us》的平均玩家人数达到30至50人<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|last=Joseph|first=Funké|date=2020-09-04|title=Why Among Us Became One of the Biggest Games on Twitch Two Years After Release|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/games/among-us/among-us-game-twitch/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909025026/https://www.pastemagazine.com/games/among-us/among-us-game-twitch/|archive-date=2020-09-09|access-date=2020-09-08|website=[[Paste_(magazine)|Paste]]|language=en}}</ref>。程序员Forest Willard认为“发行效果不佳”，设计师Marcus Bromander则认为原因在于InnerSloth工作室“在营销方面确实很糟糕”<ref name=":10" />。开发团队“多次打算放弃”，但在一小群玩家的支持下继续进行工作<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|last=Campbell|first=Amy|date=2020-09-22|title=Among Us Devs Have Created a Gaming Phenomenon, Albeit Two Years After It Launched|url=https://www.escapistmagazine.com/v2/among-us-devs-have-created-a-gaming-phenomenon-albeit-two-years-after-it-launched/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924152953/https://www.escapistmagazine.com/v2/among-us-devs-have-created-a-gaming-phenomenon-albeit-two-years-after-it-launched/|archive-date=2020-09-24|access-date=2020-09-24|website=[[The_Escapist_(magazine)|Escapist Magazine]]|language=en-US}}</ref>，先后添加了多人在线模式、新任务和自定义选项<ref name=":14" />，在这之后发布了Steam版本<ref name=":10" />。PC版本支持[[跨平台游戏|跨平台游戏]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=Power|first=Tom|date=2020-09-16|title=Is there crossplay in Among Us?|url=https://www.gamepur.com/guides/is-there-crossplay-in-among-us|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924153020/https://www.gamepur.com/guides/is-there-crossplay-in-among-us|archive-date=2020-09-24|access-date=2020-09-21|website=Gamepur|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Matthews|first=Emma|date=2020-09-10|title=How crossplay works in Among Us|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/among-us-crossplay-pc-and-mobile/|access-date=2020-09-15|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123342/https://www.pcgamer.com/among-us-crossplay-pc-and-mobile/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在2019年添加了另外两个地图「Mira HQ」和「Polus」<ref name=":11">{{Cite web|last=Coto|first=Adrian|date=2020-09-21|title=Among Us Surpasses PUBG With Almost 400,000 Concurrent Steam Players|url=https://screenrant.com/among-us-pubg-concurrent-players/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924153020/https://screenrant.com/among-us-pubg-concurrent-players/|archive-date=2020-09-24|access-date=2020-09-21|website=ScreenRant|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2019-08-08|title=MIRA HQ Launched! - Among Us by Innersloth|url=https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us/devlog/94023/mira-hq-launched|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123251/https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us/devlog/94023/mira-hq-launched|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-16|website=[[Itch.io|Itch.io]]|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2019-11-12|title=Polus Map Launched! - Among Us by Innersloth|url=https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us/devlog/109603/polus-map-launched|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123255/https://innersloth.itch.io/among-us/devlog/109603/polus-map-launched|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-16|website=[[Itch.io|Itch.io]]|language=en}}</ref>。并且在2021年3月31日添加了一个基于Henry stickmin系列的一款名叫飞艇的新地图。

根据Willard的说法，该团队坚持开发这款游戏，“比从纯粹商业角度来说的开发时间要长得多”，定期更新游戏的频率高达每周一次，这使得玩家如同雪球般的稳定增长。Bromander表示，他们之所以能够这样做是因为他们有足够的积蓄让他们在游戏销售不佳的情况下也能继续制作游戏<ref name="improb">{{Cite web|title=Among Us' Improbable Rise To The Top Of Twitch|url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/09/among-us-improbable-rise-to-the-top-of-twitch/|access-date=2020-09-08|date=2020-09-08|last=Grayson|first=Nathan|website=[[Kotaku_Australia|Kotaku Australia]]|language=en-AU|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909025025/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/09/among-us-improbable-rise-to-the-top-of-twitch/|archive-date=2020-09-09|url-status=dead}}</ref>。

=== 人气提升 ===
2020年，在韩国和巴西的二次创作者掀起了一股热潮，这股高人气的热潮甚至影响到了[[英语世界|英语世界]]。Bromander指出，游戏在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[巴西|巴西]]和[[韩国|韩国]]比美国最受欢迎<ref name="improb" /><ref name=":7" />。根据Willard的说法，因为Twitch實況主[[Sodapoppin|Sodapoppin]]该游戏于2020年7月在Twitch流行起来<ref name="improb" />。在这之后，许多Twitch實況主和YouTubers开始玩起了《Among Us》，包括著名的创作者CallMeCarson、[[xQc|xQc]]、[[Pokimane|Pokimane]]、[[麥可·格澤希克|Shroud]]、[[Ninja_(網絡紅人)|Ninja]]和[[PewDiePie|PewDiePie]]。<ref name=":15" /><ref>{{Cite web|last=Zheng|first=Jenny|date=2020-09-21|title=Among Us Is Even More Popular Than You Think Right Now|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/among-us-is-even-more-popular-than-you-think-right-now/1100-6482376/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923035935/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/among-us-is-even-more-popular-than-you-think-right-now/1100-6482376/|archive-date=2020-09-23|access-date=2020-09-24|website=GameSpot|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":16" />[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的Emma Kent认为，《Among Us》因为Innersloth的The Henry Stickmin Collection的发行而提升了知名度，<ref name=":15" />[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]的Wes Fenlon相信Twitch實況主SR_Kaif“为《Among Us》时刻做好了准备”。<ref name=":16" />在此期间，Innersloth工作室开始出售《Among Us》的周边<ref name=":4" />。

游戏在接下来的几个月人气继续升温，2020年9月游戏的下载量超过了1亿次<ref name=":16" />，玩家数量持续上升，最终达到同时在线150万名玩家<ref>* {{Cite web|last=Macgregor|first=Jody|date=2020-09-09|title=Multiplayer space mystery Among Us hits 1.5 million simultaneous players|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/multiplayer-space-mystery-among-us-hits-15-million-simultaneous-players/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123259/https://www.pcgamer.com/multiplayer-space-mystery-among-us-hits-15-million-simultaneous-players/|archive-date=2020-09-21|access-date=2020-09-12|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|language=en-US}}
